    "reply_body_html": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div dir=\"ltr\"><div>Hi Christie,</div><div><br></div><div>I apologize but I realized shortly after this that we are already working with a firm on some similar work and they've presented us with their findings that we're moving forward with.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for reaching out.</div><div><br></div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_signature\" data-smartmail=\"gmail_signature\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Tucker Pivonka (<a href=\"https://www.rexwilde.com/blog/a-quick-guide-to-sharing-pronouns-in-email-signatures\" target=\"_blank\">he/him</a>)<div>VP of Product Leadership</div><div>Crema</div><div>816.447.7228</div><div><br></div></div></div></div><br></div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote gmail_quote_container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Tue, Mar 17, 2026 at 11:36 AM Christie Johansen-Pinney &lt;<a href=\"mailto:christie@roosterpunkdigital.com\">christie@roosterpunkdigital.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex; border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204); padding-left:1ex\"><div><p>Hi Tucker,</p><p>Really glad you're interested, and thanks for sharing that context about Product Practice. That's exactly the kind of detail that helps us make the report genuinely useful rather than generic.</p><p>The angle you described (consulting organizations on the systems and humans behind the product) is a fascinating positioning challenge, especially for a service line that's still finding its home on the site. We'll make sure the Brand Trends Intelligence Report reflects what's resonating in that space so you can position Product Practice with real clarity.</p><p>We'll get straight to work on this. To help our analyst team and AI tool zero in on the most relevant areas for you, could you take a couple of minutes to fill out this short survey?</p><p><a href=\"https://roosterpunk.com/pulse\" target=\"_blank\">https://roosterpunk.com/pulse</a></p><p>And once we have the findings ready, I'd love to walk you through them on a call. You can grab a time that works for you here:</p><p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/christie-johansen-pinney-roosterpunk/rooster-punk-pulse-report-review?month=2025-12\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendly.com/christie-johansen-pinney-roosterpunk/rooster-punk-pulse-report-review?month=2025-12</a></p><p>Looking forward to digging into this.</p><p>Best,<br>Christie</p></div></blockquote></div></body></html>",
